---
title: One-Pot Asian Beef & Udon Noodle Soup with Charred Corn & Parsley
description: Warm up with the flavours of a sweet and soy beef udon soup. The broth is rich and inviting so dive your spoon in a scoop out as much udon noodles and tasty beef as you can. This soup is just the thing you needed on a winter night.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
